# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Hatters Away — LTFC Itinerary Planner
# Environment Configuration
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your Relevance AI credentials.
# CRITICAL: Never commit .env to version control (it is already in .gitignore).
# ⚠️  SECURITY: This file contains sensitive API keys and credentials
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Relevance AI Region Code
# Required: Yes 
# Notes: This identifies which regional server to use
VITE_REGION=your-region

# Relevance AI Project
# Required: Yes
# Notes: Unique identifier for your Relevance AI project
VITE_PROJECT=your-project

# LTFC Itinerary Planner Agent ID (UUID)
# Required: Yes 
# Notes: Specific agent instance for the itinerary planner
VITE_AGENT_ID=your-agent-id

# Workforce ID (Optional - Alternative routing method)
# Required: No
# Notes: Use ONLY if configured for workforce-based routing instead of agent routing
# VITE_WORKFORCE_ID=your-workforce-id

